Variables:
    are like boxes/containers which can hold data for us. we can change the data
    later on if we want. we can reuse the same variable as many times as we wan.
    there are 8 basic/primitive data types.
4 basic data types to store whole numbers.
    1)byte 2)short 3)int 4)long

2 basic data types to store decimal numbers.
    i)float ii)double

1 data type to store characters:
    char
to store ture/false
    boolean

NonPrimitives:
    1)String
        I can store works, sentence, pragraph and its most widly used data type which used.